Package: EcoSAR
Type: Package
Title: Environmental SAR Analysis Tools Using Sentinel-1 and Google Earth Engine
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Esperance", "Kandjale", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    EcoSAR provides tools to load, process, summarize,
    visualize, and extract Sentinel-1 Synthetic Aperture Radar (SAR)
    data from Google Earth Engine using the rgee package.
    The package is designed for environmental monitoring applications
    including wetlands, forests, soil moisture analysis,
    flood detection, and land cover change studies.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rgee
